description: As Always Great quality and design by shany, this elegant, aluminium case is made of high quality material for long lasting with durable Snake skin color and texture. unlike other brands SHANY have used aluminium on the handle, as well as the bottom of the case to ensure a long life time. trays are made of plastic with adjustable dividers, which can be adjusted to almost 20" and you can fit your biggest brushes in there as well. SHANY trademark and logo is printed on the box and handles .
title: SHANY Snake Skin Pink Aluminium Train Case with Shoulder Strap, 4-Pounds
